# --- Secret / credential hardening ---
# Defensive guards against ever committing signing material or credentials to a
# public repository. None of these are tracked today; the patterns exist so an
# accidental `git add` of a real keystore or key file is caught by Git itself.
*.jks
*.keystore
*.p12
*.pfx
keystore.properties
signing.properties
secrets.properties
*.pem
*.key

# Heap dumps and profiling captures may embed in-memory secrets / user data.
*.hprof

# Roborazzi / Kover leftover artifacts from local screenshot diffing.
*-actual.png
*_actual.png

# NOTE — intentionally tracked, do NOT add to this file:
#   * app/google-services.json                          — placeholder Firebase
#     config (project_id "android-ai-agent-placeholder", zeroed project_number,
#     placeholder API key) required for local & CI builds; carries no real
#     Firebase identifiers or secrets.
#   * app/src/main/assets/universal_sentence_encoder.tflite — bundled on-device
#     USE embedding model, the default embedding provider; required at runtime.